Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.57,0:00:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小桃  爷爷  那我就走咯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.15,0:00:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一路走好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.70,0:00:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  Summer School要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.49,0:00:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.62,0:00:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我出门咯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.41,0:00:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.71,0:00:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们也开始作战吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.59,0:00:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呐  爷爷  真的要做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.01,0:00:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.14,0:00:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出发吧  小桃队员
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.28,0:02:20.99,Disp,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,289)\fad(500,0)}式根岛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.99,0:02:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}（欢迎来到式根岛）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到咯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.92,0:02:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来到式根岛  发现海的颜色都不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.71,0:02:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟距离大岛有50公里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.47,0:02:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是天气这么好真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.47,0:02:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.19,0:02:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全员  朝着目标的旅馆出发
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:02:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.11,0:02:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大海好漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}要是买了新泳衣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一色同学  二叶同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三枝同学  四宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.70,0:03:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍等下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们把Operation Key都交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.58,0:03:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全员的钥匙都由我来保管
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.67,0:03:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们的钥匙与世界的命运息息相关
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.09,0:03:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在海里弄掉了就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.89,0:03:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水羽老师说的很对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.35,0:03:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.56,0:03:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在Summer School结束前我会统一保管
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  你们可以出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.27,0:03:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们出发啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Valkyria-1呼叫WildVizell
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.49,0:03:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是Valkyria-1
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WildVizell请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WildVizell呼叫Valkyria-1　敏感度良好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,报告  按照预定回收了全员的Operation Key
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.38,0:03:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:03:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么现在开始作战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.13,0:04:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个  一色博士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.13,0:04:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些真的是为了她们好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次的Summer School
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是强化小茜她们友情力量的千载良机
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.31,0:04:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就看着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老夫的特训计划是完美的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特训计划啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  向日葵你的泳衣好可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.42,0:04:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常合身哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.05,0:04:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.26,0:04:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看  跟我说的一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶  什么什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个是之前两人去买的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.35,0:04:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟若叶一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.18,0:04:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为她说没有泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:04:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然也想过借我的给她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确实若叶的泳衣的话  装不下向日葵的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.61,0:05:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔  软软弹弹的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说…小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小茜！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.29,0:05:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.75,0:05:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summer School终归是学习的一环
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.84,0:05:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先考虑着环境问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.67,0:05:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包含着对照顾我们的这片海岸的感谢之情捡垃圾吧
