Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.19,0:21:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.28,0:21:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.65,0:21:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有事…
